This is the Hybrid_Comm-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the Hybrid_Comm blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'Hybrid_Comm', which is imported as:

    import Hybrid_Comm

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(Hybrid_Comm)
